# Vet Chatbot Project (Backend + Frontend SDK)

This project contains the backend server and the frontend embeddable SDK
for the Vet Chatbot.

---

## BACKEND

Backend is built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

Backend responsibilities:

- Handle chat messages
- Handle appointments
- Connect to MongoDB
- Provide APIs for frontend and SDK

---

## BACKEND TECHNOLOGIES

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- dotenv
- CORS

---

## BACKEND FOLDER STRUCTURE

backend/
|
|-- index.js
|-- package.json
|-- .env
|
|-- src/
|-- modules/
|-- chat/
| |-- chat.controller.js
| |-- chat.service.js
| |-- chat.routes.js
| |-- chat.model.js
|
|-- appointment/
|-- appointment.controller.js
|-- appointment.service.js
|-- appointment.routes.js
|-- appointment.model.js

---

## BACKEND SETUP

Step 1: Go to backend folder

cd backend

Step 2: Install dependencies

npm install

Step 3: Create .env file

PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/vet_chatbot

Step 4: Start server

npm run dev

Server will start on:

http://localhost:5000

---

## BACKEND TEST

Health check URL:

http://localhost:5000/health

Response:

{
"status": "OK"
}

---

## API ROUTES

POST /api/chat  
POST /api/appointments

---

## COMMON BACKEND ISSUES

MongoDB not connected:

- Make sure MongoDB is running
- Check MONGO_URI in .env

Server not starting:

- Run npm install
- Use Node version 18 or above

---

## FRONTEND + SDK

Frontend is a React application that can also be built as an embeddable SDK.

SDK can be used on any website using a script tag.

---

## FRONTEND TECHNOLOGIES

- React
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript

---

## FRONTEND FOLDER STRUCTURE

frontend/chatbot-sdk/
|
|-- sdk/
| |-- index.jsx
| |-- App.jsx
| |-- style.css
|
|-- dist/
| |-- vet-chatbot-sdk.iife.js
| |-- vet-chatbot-sdk.css
|
|-- vite.sdk.config.js
|-- tailwind.config.js
|-- package.json

---

## FRONTEND SETUP

Step 1: Go to frontend folder

cd frontend/chatbot-sdk

Step 2: Install dependencies

npm install

Step 3: Run frontend locally

npm run dev

Open browser:

http://localhost:5173

---

## BUILD SDK

Command to build SDK:

npm run build:sdk

package.json script:

"scripts": {
"build:sdk": "vite build --config vite.sdk.config.js"
}

After build, files will be generated in dist folder.

---

## USE SDK ON ANY WEBSITE

Add CSS:

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://vet-chat-bot-liard.vercel.app/vet-chatbot-sdk.css" />

Add Script:

<script src="https://vet-chat-bot-liard.vercel.app/vet-chatbot-sdk.iife.js"></script>

Chatbot will load automatically.

---

## LOCAL SDK TEST

Create index.html:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>SDK Test</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./dist/vet-chatbot-sdk.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello</h1>
    <script src="./dist/vet-chatbot-sdk.iife.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>

Open with Live Server.

---

## COMMON SDK ISSUES

process is not defined:

- Fixed by using IIFE build format

SDK not visible:

- Make sure CSS file is loaded
- Make sure script URL is correct

---

